I think you're eating
khash today.

746
00:38:03,211 --> 00:38:04,972
Said to be a hangover cure.

747
00:38:05,006 --> 00:38:06,491
That's it, yeah.

748
00:38:06,525 --> 00:38:09,010
It's made out of
legs of cows, I think.

749
00:38:09,045 --> 00:38:11,358
Cool, I like legs of cows.

750
00:38:11,392 --> 00:38:12,359
I like their eyes.

751
