we say "khash."

773
00:39:18,079 --> 00:39:20,012
It means just boiled.
Right.

774
00:39:20,047 --> 00:39:22,394
So there is big debate whether
it's Georgian or Armenian.

775
00:39:22,429 --> 00:39:24,914
Of course, every Armenian
is sure it's Armenian.

776
00:39:24,948 --> 00:39:28,193
What are you talking about?
What are you talking about?

